Falador shield is a reward from completing parts of the Falador Diary. There are four types, depending on which part of the diary the player has completed. Those are:

  • Falador shield 1, from the easy tasks set
  • Falador shield 2, from the medium tasks set
  • Falador shield 3, from the hard tasks set
  • Falador shield 4, from the elite tasks set

'''Falador shield''' is a reward from completing parts of the [[Falador Diary]]. There are four types, depending on which part of the diary the player has completed. Those are:

*[[Falador shield 1]], from the easy tasks set
*[[Falador shield 2]], from the medium tasks set
*[[Falador shield 3]], from the hard tasks set
*[[Falador shield 4]], from the elite tasks set
